    AutomationSystemForCargoCompany.Branch
    public class AutomationSystemForCargoCompany.Branch.BranchEmployee
extends AutomationSystemForCargoCompany.User
    Branch Employee can add and remove Customers to the system Add and remove shipments for a branch, update status of the Shipment sent from that branch It is an inner class of Branch since it is only responsible for functionality of a branch, would not exist without a branch
